flowchart LR
  subgraph client [Client side]
    U[User runs cmd] --> A[Agent spawns hook]
  end
  A -->|stdin pipe| B["entire hooks<br/>session-start"]
  B --> C[io.ReadAll blocks on EOF]
  C -->|EOF| OK[Parse + dispatch]
  C -->|no EOF| STUCK[Hang]
  STUCK -->|killed| FAIL[No session logged]
  FAIL -->|user retries| U
